  ('bookkeeper-moex-00598', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-109-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲公司生產標準化產品，7月份有關成本資料如下，請問應分攤至產品成本之製造費用總額為何？ 直接材料$100,000，工廠電費$20,000，間接人工$70,000，辦公大樓租金$60,000，間接材料$50,000， 直接人工$90,000，利息費用$40,000', '["$140,000", "$200,000", "$330,000", "$390,000"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7ef2feb8ffc4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4239d9d0a8f0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109180", "c": "602", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年專技人員高等考試建築師、32類科技師(含第二次食品技師)、大地工程技師考試分階段考試(第二階段考試)暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00599', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-109-d35177eb', 'sub-bookkeeper-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '乙公司生產甲產品一批，其製造成本為$100,000，主要成本為$70,000，製造費用為直接材料成本 之75%，該批產品之加工成本為何？', '["$70,000", "$60,000", "$40,000", "$30,000"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7ef2feb8ffc4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "4239d9d0a8f0", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109180", "c": "602", "s": "1301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "會計學概要", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年專技人員高等考試建築師、32類科技師(含第二次食品技師)、大地工程技師考試分階段考試(第二階段考試)暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
